@node Introduction
@chapter Introduction

@strong{3DViewer} is a cross-platform application for viewing and analyzing 3D models in OBJ format.  
The project supports basic affine transformations, visualization, as well as unit testing and code coverage.

@node Quick Start
@chapter Quick Start

@section Requirements

@itemize
@item GCC >= 9 or Clang >= 10
@item Qt5 (qtbase5-dev, qt5-qmake, qtchooser)
@item GoogleTest (libgtest-dev)
@item lcov, valgrind, texinfo, texlive (for tests and documentation)
@end itemize

@section Build

@enumerate
@item Install dependencies:
@example
sudo apt update
sudo apt install gcc g++ qtbase5-dev qt5-qmake qtchooser libgtest-dev lcov valgrind texinfo texlive
@end example

@item Build the project:
@example
make
@end example

@item Run the application:
@example
./3DViewer
@end example

@item Run tests:
@example
make tests
@end example

@item Generate documentation:
@example
make dvi
@end example
@end enumerate

