@node Usage
@chapter Usage

@section Loading Models

The application supports loading OBJ format files.  
To load a model, use the application menu or the controller function:

@example
Controller ctrl;
NormalizationParameters params = {0.0f, 1.0f, 1.0f, 1.0f};
ctrl.LoadFromFile("model.obj", params);
@end example

@section Affine Transformations

Scaling, translation, and rotation are available:

@example
ctrl.MoveScene(1.0, 0.0, 0.0);    // Move along X
ctrl.RotateScene(0.0, 0.0, 3.14); // Rotate around Z
ctrl.ScaleScene(2.0, 2.0, 2.0);   // Scale
@end example

@section Keyboard Controls

@itemize
@item Leff Arrow, Right Arrow — move along X
@item Up Arrow, Down Arrow — move along Y
@item Q, E — rotation
@item Mouse Scroll — scaling
@end itemize

